#- THE AUSCHWITZ ACT

From now to when either Polynesia and its greatness falls or until this great National Socialist Empire decrees otherwise, all jews are not allowed on Polynesian soil for any reason.
#- ARTICLES

1a. Self admitted jews are in no way shape or form allowed on Polynesian soil without approval from the Polynesian government.

1b. This no-jew rule also applies to shitposters who claim to be jews for bantz.
#- 2a. No jewish acts, traditions, or holidays are to be celebrated on Polynesian soil.

2b. Also applies to non-jews who celebrate jewish holidays.
#- 3a. No jews are allowed to sell or buy on Polynesian land. No acts of usury or fraud by anyone, especially jews.

